<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA621_02_SU_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    
    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />
    
    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="../../common_contents/js/ema621_02_0003.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema621_02.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema621_02_su_0003">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1" class="fraction_box_title">
          <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
              과학 기지의 식물 공장에서 비료
              <span class="fraction_box"><span>7</span><span>10</span></span
              >㎏을 화분 한 개에 <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>10</span></span
              >㎏씩 나누어 주려고 합니다. 비료를 화분 몇 개에 나누어 줄 수 있는지 알아
            </div>
            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">봅시다.</div>
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <div class="img_row flex align_start">
          <div class="picture_wrap">
            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA621_02_SU/0003_content.png" alt="자치회 활동 이미지" />
            <button class="zoom"></button>
          </div>

          <div class="input_area">
            <article class="page page_1">
              <h3 lang="y">구하는 식을 써 보세요.</h3>
              <div class="question_box justify_center">
                <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="(7)/(10)÷(1)/(10)"></math-field>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_2">
              <h3 lang="y">
                <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                  <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                    <span class="fraction_box ml_0"><span>7</span><span>10</span></span
                    >㎏ 을 그림에 나타내고, <span class="fraction_box"><span>7</span><span>10</span></span>㎏ 은 <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>10</span></span>
                    이 몇 개인지 알아
                  </div>
                  <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">보세요.</div>
                </div>
              </h3>
              <div class="question_box justify_center">
                <div class="box box1">
                  <span class="tag">예</span>
                  <div class="txt txt1">
                    <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>10</span></span>
                    <span lang="y">㎏</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="boolean_count_wrap col" data-answer-single="7">
                    <button></button>
                    <button></button>
                    <button></button>
                    <button></button>
                    <button></button>
                    <button></button>
                    <button></button>
                    <button></button>
                    <button></button>
                    <button></button>
                  </div>
                  <span class="txt txt2" lang="y">1(㎏)</span>
                  <span class="txt txt3" lang="y">0</span>
                </div>
                <div class="box box2">
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="7"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <span lang="y" class="f32b">개</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_3">
              <h3 lang="y">
                <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                  <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                    <span class="fraction_box ml_0"><span>7</span><span>10</span></span
                    >㎏ 에서 <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>10</span></span>㎏ 을 몇 번 덜어 낼 수 있나요?
                  </div>
                </div>
              </h3>
              <div class="question_box justify_center">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="7"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span lang="y" class="f32b">번</span>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_4">
                <h3 lang="y">                
                    <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                      <div class="fraction_txt">
                          <span class="fraction_box ml_0"><span>7</span><span>10</span></span
                          >&divide;<span class="fraction_box ml_0"><span>1</span><span>10</span></span> 은 얼마인가요?
                        </div>
                      </div>
                  </h3>
                  <div class="question_box justify_center">
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="7"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_5">
                <h3 lang="y">비료를 화분 몇 개에 나누어 줄 수 있나요?</h3>
                  <div class="question_box justify_center">
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="7"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    <span lang="y" class="f32b">개</span>
                  </div>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
        

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <!-- <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button> -->
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
